name: C-Mecha Musume C素体机娘
description:
Thanks to the original author 搞事德·乔斯达's wonderful thought and generosity, now C-Mecha Musume is released on Civitai.

感谢原作者搞事德·乔斯达的奇思妙想和慷慨大方，C素体机娘在Civitai上发布了。

More Mecha。

更为机械化。

He recommend giving a try to adding clothing tags.

他推荐试试加上服装tag。

Suggested Weight（推荐权重）：0.4~1.0.
